022package com.restfb.webhook;
023
024import java.util.Date;
025
026import com.restfb.types.webhook.messaging.*;
027
028/**
029 * interface to provide methods a listener can implement to handle the different messaging items
030 */
031public interface WebhookMessagingListener {
032
033  void accountLinking(final AccountLinkingItem item, MessagingParticipant recipient, MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
034
035  void appRoles(final AppRoles appRoles, MessagingParticipant recipient, MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
036
037  void checkoutUpdate(final CheckoutUpdateItem checkoutUpdate, MessagingParticipant recipient,
038                      MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
039
040  void delivery(final DeliveryItem delivery, MessagingParticipant recipient, MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
041
042  void message(final MessageItem message, MessagingParticipant recipient, MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
043
044  void optin(final OptinItem optin, MessagingParticipant recipient, MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
045
046  void passThreadControl(final PassThreadControlItem passThreadControl, MessagingParticipant recipient,
047                         MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
048
049  void payment(final PaymentItem payment, MessagingParticipant recipient, MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
050
051  void policyEnforcement(final PolicyEnforcementItem policyEnforcement, MessagingParticipant recipient,
052                         MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
053
054  void postback(final PostbackItem postback, MessagingParticipant recipient, MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
055
056  void reaction(final MessageReaction reaction, MessagingParticipant recipient, MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
057
058  void read(final ReadItem read, MessagingParticipant recipient, MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
059
060  void referral(final ReferralItem referral, MessagingParticipant recipient, MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
061
062  void requestThreadControl(final RequestThreadControlItem requestThreadControl, MessagingParticipant recipient,
063                            MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
064
065  void takeThreadControl(final TakeThreadControlItem takeThreadControl, MessagingParticipant recipient,
066                         MessagingParticipant sender, Date timestamp);
067}
